00:28:10,522 --> 00:28:11,597
It calls for a drink, right?

528
00:28:13,358 --> 00:28:14,660
Hurry up and order it.

529
00:28:14,726 --> 00:28:16,161
-Alcohol…
-"Hurry up and order it."

530
00:28:16,228 --> 00:28:18,330
-Order it.
-Next is alcohol.

