to go for a second round.

558
00:30:10,042 --> 00:30:12,978
Can I eat and drink a little more?

559
00:30:13,045 --> 00:30:15,080
-Of course.
-This place is the best.

560
00:30:15,147 --> 00:30:16,448
Have you had a lot already?

561
00:30:16,548 --> 00:30:20,118
No. I can drink at least ten times more.

562
00:30:20,185 --> 00:30:21,219
Amazing.

563
00:30:21,286 --> 00:30:23,789
You are a great son.

564
00:30:24,356 --> 00:30:27,726
